Class ClassSchedule

java.lang.Object
gymmanager.gymproject3.ClassSchedule
public class ClassSchedule extends Object
Used to create new ClassSchedule objects that hold all fitness classes at all gym locations, and the number of classes.
Author:
Aaron Newland, Dylan Pina
